{"title":"Favorite fiction of 2024","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/908395844/0/marginalrevolution~Favorite-fiction-of.html","date":1732516530000,"content":"<p>Itamar Vieira Junior, <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.amazon.com/Crooked-Plow-Novel-Verso-Fiction/dp/1839766409/ref=sr_1_1?crid=3MEQEGK3JMHG0&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9._kEdPTEL7Ctic0DjdPg_MfwE74KOaQUp9gnVESh6-bfGjHj071QN20LucGBJIEps.mdNtZMnLYGhGS1O6E9140dBtBfOa6xUJMHfzLa2wWbY&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=crooked+plow%2C+by+itamar+vieira+junior&amp;qid=1732109706&amp;sprefix=crooked+plow%2Caps%2C347&amp;sr=8-1\" target=\"_blank\">Crooked Plow</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Karen Jennings, <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.amazon.com/Crooked-Seeds-Novel-Karen-Jennings/dp/0593597125\" target=\"_blank\">Crooked Seeds</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Richard Flanagan, <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.amazon.com/Question-7-Richard-Flanagan/dp/0593802330/ref=sr_1_1?crid=1ET48ONQPKKZ7&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9._AE3ZnbP57xRWitD0JA3UFQCNMOFIlWYVh-NZYov7irYiHd1z-lnEenl6ciTDY0Yagw_wj4oteKo9vD_YhrODg.YwsKmpMF5WBR_F5CyHYnxiHhqeBoEFTkqmcie73J8PE&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=question+seven+flanagan&amp;qid=1732109739&amp;sprefix=question+seven%2Caps%2C372&amp;sr=8-1\" target=\"_blank\">Question Seven</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Guadalupe Nettel, <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.amazon.com/hija-%C3%BAnica-Narrativas-hisp%C3%A1nicas-Spanish/dp/8433999060/ref=sr_1_1?crid=3IIW9Z6EJO9RD&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.4J8yPu-22UYUyK_4BJ4O3_em9SKCHVZFmLrw9ajD30jGjHj071QN20LucGBJIEps.s0_bHBMYtxirrkM5EL4M0cSFmI-0Ag0DpI9wjHxmtQM&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=Guadalupe+Nettel%2C+La+hija+%C3%BAnica&amp;qid=1732109773&amp;sprefix=guadalupe+nettel%2C+la+hija+%C3%BAnica%2Caps%2C649&amp;sr=8-1\" target=\"_blank\">La hija única</a>, or<i> Still Born</i></p>\r\n<p>Sally Rooney, <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.amazon.com/Intermezzo-Novel-Sally-Rooney/dp/0374602638/ref=sr_1_1?crid=1X3PQXN1QQ2GA&amp;dib=eyJ2IjoiMSJ9.3Z6W5p_X9alnvbOR_YQ976f8-LrATH1vPEhS0z_HhqITBFgBathlz2z_BrMYFU3bPha-TMTJvIGjmLOhBl9_SNrku5h6bJ0BjMdBAiqcvOyF1ER0FfB9OeNR2c4itbahiv4skYswA3eJUU_E30ZkqKg3aCGyoU4P-B5bqNxrsvZQZDkso_x6jt5lEJsV-ykgh2RXAcgCpJ9-JV5OxcReJXIGgBqzhKEDtMsEdoh8kag.MIWCpwD5FPgiEnG_0hDnTODu0xss0LRBVDemfLZvuSo&amp;dib_tag=se&amp;keywords=sally+rooney&amp;qid=1732109810&amp;sprefix=sally+rooney%2Caps%2C375&amp;sr=8-1\" target=\"_blank\">Intermezzo</a>.  Here is <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.commonreader.co.uk/p/neurodivergence-and-normal-people\" target=\"_blank\">a good Henry Oliver review</a>.</p>\r\n<p>Of those I would pick <em>Crooked Plow</em> as the best.  The new novels by Alan Hollinghurst and Murakami stand some chance of making the list.  I will start them soon, and report back if I like them.</p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/11/favorite-fiction-of-2024.html\">Favorite fiction of 2024</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/908395844/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/908395844/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/908395844/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/908395844/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/x.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/19/908395844/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedbl